        <title>2025-06-15全球焦点：量子突破、气候协议、脑机接口</title>
        <link>https://blog.hambook.top/p/2025-06-15%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%84%A6%E7%82%B9%E9%87%8F%E5%AD%90%E7%AA%81%E7%A0%B4%E6%B0%94%E5%80%99%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E8%84%91%E6%9C%BA%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%A3/</link>
